EmailTemplate.subject: St Andrew's Cathedral School
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
In the meantime, I have attached some information regarding our Junior School:
· An overview of our supportive learning culture for all students;
· A co-curricular booklet that provides details of the various out-of-class activities available for students; and
· Our fantastic music program that offers opportunity for involvement at any grade;
· An article written by our Head of Junior School, Mrs Rhonda Robson on Why we value singing at St Andrew’s;
· An article about a regular visitor to the Junior School – the Surfing Scientist, Reuben Meerman;
· An article about the greening of our rooftop garden by Junior School students; and
· A video clip of our Junior School students in action.
You can keep up-to-date with what’s happening at the School via our Facebook page and you can view more videos on our official YouTube channel.
If I can be of any further assistance, please feel free to contact me directly on 9286 9552.
Regards
Robyn
